quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  11,46,"O daali: "Ko an yo Nuuhu, pellet on jeyaaka e …ďeynguure maa, nden (toraare) ko gollal ngal mo∆ī∆īaa. Wata a toro kam ko a alanaa …óum ganndal. min mi…óo waajo maa fii wata a jeye e majju…ďe …ďeen"."
  11,47,"O maaki: "Joomi am, mi moolorike ma nde mi lanndoto maa huunde nde mi alanah …óum ganndal. Si wanaa A hafranam yurmin ∆äaa mi, mi jeyete e hayru…ďe …ďen"(.pertu…ďe)"
  11,48,"Wi'aa: "Ko an yo Nuuhu, jippor kisiyee immorde ka amen, e mo∆ī∆īi dow maa…óaa e mofte won¬īdu…ďe e maa…óa. Mofte goo (no ton), aray min dakmita …ďe, refti memoya …ďe immorde e amen, lepte muus…óe"."
  11,49,"∆äii …óoo ko jeyaa…ói e kabaruuji birnii…ói, mi…óen wahayina …óe e maa…óa. A anndaano …óe an, wanaa yim…ďe maa …ďen, ko adii …óum. Mu√Ī√Īo, pellet battane mo∆ī∆īe …óen woanii gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďen."
  11,50,"[minn Nulii] kadi faade e Aadinkoo…ďe …ďen, musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on Huudi. O maaki : "eeheymon yo yim…ďe am, ndewee Alla, dewetee…óo alanah on ko woori mo. On ngonaani si wonaa fekindotoo…ďe"."
  11,51,"Eeheymon yim…ďe am, mi la…ďndaaki on e …óuum njo…ďdi. Njo…ďdi am wonaani si wonaa ka on tak…óo lam. En on haqqiltaa?"
  11,52,"Eheymon yim…ďe am, imsinee ka Joomi mon, refti tuubanon mo o jippina e moo…óon to…ďo jokkondirn-ngo, o …ďeyda on cemmbe e hoore cemmbe mon …óen. Wota on nduŇčto ngono ko on bon…ďe."
  11,53,"∆Āe mbi'i: "eheymaHuudu, kala ko addan-…óaa men e …ďanngannduyee, minen men wonaani accoo…ďe dewetee…ói amen …óin fii konngol maa ngol, minen min ngonaani gooŇč…óinoo…ďe ma"."